HEADWORD: Renumerate
<hw>Re*nu"mer*ate</hw> <pr>(r?-n?"m?r-?t)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>renumeratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>renumerare</ets> to count
over, count up; pref. <ets>re-</ets> re- + <ets>numerare</ets> to count.
See <er>Numerate</er>.]</ety> <def>To recount.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

